It seems that the enemy is about to use
a powerful technique, but this is
actually a good opportunity!

If we can blind them when they launch
their next attack, we'll have a chance
to win!

I'll give it my all!

Slime's suit caused an overflow and

Guehehe, useless! I can split as many

Guehehe, useless! I can split as many

Ah... I can't reach the attack again.

name: 媚薬怪人フェロモニア

parameters:

What is this concentration!? This is

I won't lose anymore with this!

impossible to purify.

pheromones with such junk is
impossible!

Guh... You nymphomaniac! If that's how
it's going to be, then I'll give it my
all! More, I need to release even more
pheromones...!
